name: Anc in Orbit
description: (mp3 14min 51sec) Music for the Arhanta Comics Series: "OLIMAX, Deep Space Cartographer". BClune on synthesizers, @camilographics on moog and electric guitar. Recorded in Ithaca, NY 2017 through 2021. ~Searching for warm treasures, from far out in the cold vastness of space~ Anc (probe) depicted on cover image is a custom design by the mysterious space tycoon, Bhazil Khealune (probe #bhk342lp9).
